"That I can & will. I plan to return to the Ark as soon as I have met with 
the Decepticons here on this continent. We shall bring them back to the Base.. 
if.. that is what you wish," the last couple words a little more sultry as she 
was wishing to please him. She always has wanted to, ever since she laid 
optics upon him for the first time. To be the best warrior, to do whatever he 
asked, to do it beyond any ability... why? .. because, she love him. 

--part1_104.2f4329d7.2c05b427_boundary
